<item>
            <title>[SYNAPSE-686] Issue when using the DynamicLordBalancingEndpoint to handl REST message.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-686</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When you try to load balance REST message, the path section is repeated in the toAddress.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;e.d&lt;br/&gt;
original URI&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:8280/example/index.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://localhost:8280/example/index.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When synapse send the message to the actual endpoint, URI become something like following.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:8280/example/index.html/example/index.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://localhost:8280/example/index.html/example/index.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In the DynamicLoadBalancingEndpoint we create an Endpoint for each and every request and set the complete URI as the to address.  &lt;/p&gt;</description>
